Story:

A mountain guy got a crush on a beautiful girl while she was visiting the mountain. As many coincidental circumstances happened to them, the guy started thinking that the girl also loved him. But, all of the matter was just his one-sided love affair. When the girl returned to Bangkok, the guy and his friends started touring Bangkok to find the girl, but ended up encountering hilarious chaos in the city.
